sentence: What courses are required for the major but not in the EECS department ?
sentence-with-vars: What courses are required for the major but not in the department0 department ?
sql: SELECT COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 , PROGRAM AS PROGRAMalias0 , PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT <> "EECS" AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID = COURSEalias0.COURSE_ID AND PROGRAMalias0.PROGRAM_ID = PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.PROGRAM_ID ;
